[SN]TITLE[SN]
Funeral for Jac Davies, four, killed in Alltwen house fire

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The funeral of a four-year-old who died in a house fire in Neath Port Talbot has taken place.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Jac Davies died following the blaze at his family's home in Alltwen, near Pontardawe, on 27 July.
His mother Jennifer Davies, 28, managed to escape with her 11-month-old baby and daughter Kelsey, six, while son Riley, three, was rescued.
An inquest into Jac's death was opened and adjourned earlier this month.
